                      HOW TO INSTALL THIS TESSA FRONTEND

 1. Build the gloox bindings. See this page for instructions:
    <http://code.google.com/p/tessa/wiki/BuildingGlooxBindings>
 2. Put the gloox.so file in this directory.
 3. Enter this directory.
 4. ./configure && make
 5. Run momple from this directory, not from src/.
